OpenAi response for Prompt : Jarvis write a letter to Boss for leave 
*****************


Dear [Boss's Name],

I am writing to inform you that I am taking a leave from [start date] to [end date].

I am taking this leave to attend to some personal matters. I understand that this leave may cause some difficulty with regards to the projects that I am working on.

I will ensure that all tasks for these projects are completed before taking my leave. I will be available by [phone, email, etc.] if any further help is required.

Thank you for your consideration.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]